---
tags: pages
title: Anonymous report
description: Contact us in the event of a violation of our Code of Conduct
layout: layouts/base.njk
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
content: |
  London CSS is dedicated to a harassment-free event for everyone. If you'd like to give feedback anonymously about a situation please use the form bellow. 
  
  We won’t be able to follow up with you directly, but we will fully investigate and take appropriate action to prevent a recurrence.
---

<header class="content__header">
  <h1 class="title page__title">
    {{ title }}
  </h1>
</header>

<article class="bg copy page__content page__content--stretch">
  {{ content | markdown | safe }}

  <form
    class="form form--stretch"
    name="coc-report"
    method="POST"
    netlify-honeypot="slip"
    data-netlify="true"
    action="/success-message"
  >
    <label class="hidden">
      Don’t fill this out if you're human:
      <input name="slip" />
    </label>

    <label for="message">Message:</label>
    <textarea name="report" id="message" required="true"></textarea>

    <button class="title register">
      <span class="register__label">Send</span>
      <svg class="icon" role="img">
        <use href="#icon-chevron-right"></use>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </form>
</article>


